text: While we didn't interact with Lisa in person, she was friendly and accommodating through AirBNB. The place was very unique-- Lots of stuff within a walking distance, and the house was pretty funky and cool! It was nice exploring Austin and having a fully detached and private house to come "home" to. The location made it really easy to get around East Austin, and Downtown.
title: Eastside Bungalow SXSW/dwntwn
